{% macro historic_documents_content() %}
  <p>
    This is a historic tribunal. The functions of this tribunal have been transferred to
    the General Regulatory Chamber of the First-tier Tribunal starting in 2010. The GRC
    began transferring records to Find Case Law in 2022. To view an archived version of
    the decisions of this tribunal the {{ link(content="UK Government Web Archive", href="https://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/ukgwa/20121102163111/http://www.informationtribunal.gov.uk/Public/search.aspx", attrs={"target": "_blank"}) }}.
  </p>
{% endmacro %}
